    {
      "type": "content",
      "content": {
        "title": {
          "english": "General Greeting: Hello / Peace be upon you"
        },
        "text": "The most common and respectful greeting in Darija, suitable for any time of day and any situation, is 'As-salamu alaykum'. It literally means 'Peace be upon you'. The standard response is 'Wa alaykum as-salam', meaning 'And upon you be peace'.",
        "examples": [
          {
            "arabic": "السَّلَامُ عَلَيْكُمْ",
            "english": "Hello / Peace be upon you (greeting)",
            "transliteration": "As-salamu alaykum"
          },
          {
            "arabic": "وَعَلَيْكُمُ السَّلَامْ",
            "english": "And upon you be peace (response)",
            "transliteration": "Wa alaykum as-salam"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "content",
      "content": {
        "title": {
          "english": "Morning Greeting: Good Morning"
        },
        "text": "To greet someone specifically in the morning, you can say 'Sabah lkhir'. The common response is 'Sabah nnoor', which literally means 'morning of light'.",
        "examples": [
          {
            "arabic": "صَبَاح الْخِيرْ",
            "english": "Good morning",
            "transliteration": "Sabah lkhir"
          },
          {
            "arabic": "صَبَاح النُّورْ",
            "english": "Morning of light (response to 'good morning')",
            "transliteration": "Sabah nnoor"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "content",
      "content": {
        "title": {
          "english": "Evening Greeting: Good Evening"
        },
        "text": "Similarly, for an evening greeting, you say 'Massa lkhir'. The response follows the same pattern as the morning greeting: 'Massa nnoor'.",
        "examples": [
          {
            "arabic": "مَسَاء الْخِيرْ",
            "english": "Good evening",
            "transliteration": "Massa lkhir"
          },
          {
            "arabic": "مَسَاء النُّورْ",
            "english": "Evening of light (response to 'good evening')",
            "transliteration": "Massa nnoor"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
