        "title": {
          "english": "Asking 'How are you?' (to a female)"
        },
        "text": "To ask a female 'How are you?', the phrase changes slightly to 'Kif dayra?'. 'Lbas?' remains the same for females as it is gender-neutral.",
        "examples": [
          {
            "arabic": "كِيفْ دَايْرَة؟",
            "english": "How are you? (to a female)",
