            "english": "I'm good, thanks to God.",
            "transliteration": "Bikhir, lhamdoulillah."
          },
          {
            "arabic": "غَايَة.",
            "english": "Great / Fine.",
            "transliteration": "Ghayya."
          },
          {
            "arabic": "كُلْشِي مْزْيَانْ.",
            "english": "Everything is good / well.",
            "transliteration": "Kolshi mzyan."
